thread.title: Irene Reading
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Irene Reading

author: Irene Reading
title: Irene Reading
text:
We travelled from Christchurch to Blenheim in 2 weeks & this trusty car didn't miss a beat.
It was spacious enough for 2 large cases & smaller travel bags, went well up mountains & had enough power for overtaking when required.
We couldn't fault our experience with Omega.
